# File: docs/8.x/urls.md, line: 112
#. type: Plain text
msgid "To verify that an incoming request has a valid signature, you should call the `hasValidSignature` method on the incoming `Request`:"
msgstr "若要驗證連入的 Request 有正確的簽名，可在連入 `Request` 中呼叫 `hasValidSignature` 方法："

# File: docs/8.x/urls.md, line: 114
# File: docs/master/urls.md, line: 114
#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "    use Illuminate\\Http\\Request;\n"
